               3. Responsive grid
            </h4>
            <p>
                Fractional and percentage-based columns can be modified to apply at particular breakpoints by prefixing classnames with  [ small- ], [ medium- ], or [ large- ].
            </p>
            <p>
                Resize the browser window horizontally to see the effect of the prefixes.
            </p>
