<p>
    <strong>
        Example of a responsive fractional grid:
    </strong>
</p>

<div class='[ grid grid--center ]'>
    <div class="grid-debug [ col large-quarter medium-half ]">
        [ col <br /> large-quarter <br />medium-half ]
    </div>
    <div class="grid-debug [ col large-three-quarters medium-half ]">
        [ col <br /> large-three-quarters <br />medium-half ]
    </div>
</div>

<p>
    <strong>
        Example of a responsive percentage grid:
    </strong>
</p>

<div class='[ grid grid--center ]'>
    <div class="grid-debug [ col large-4 medium-7 small-5 ]">
        [ col <br /> large-4 <br />medium-7 <br />small-5 ]
    </div>
    <div class="grid-debug [ col large-6 medium-3 small-5 ]">
        [ col <br /> large-6 <br />medium-7 <br />small-5 ]
    </div>
</div>
